# Shared gow-collection base image (Fedora). Pinned to a digest published to
# our own GHCR, which (unlike the upstream Fedora registry) retains old digests,
# so this pin never rots. The digest is bumped automatically by the base-image
# update flow whenever a new base is published.
BASE_APP_IMAGE=ghcr.io/baz00k/gow-collection/base:edge@sha256:12ffbc30d10e3365e8961fe296907d47a9af3fce90a2631a1ed36be5caa96137

